This tool is made to erase (completely) the memory on a HD

To use it on the empty space of your disk :
	- Create a file taking all the available space
	- Execute "./erase" on the file (with your options)

To use it on an hard drive (your data won't be recoverable) :
	- Double check the HD you want to erase (no warnings)
	- Execute erase.sh with your options
	- The disk will be format as MS/DOS with 1 FAT partition
